text: Apnay hath ko apnay girbaan mein daal woh baghair kisi qisam kay rog kay chamakta hua niklay ga bilkul safaid aur khof say (bachney kay liye) apnay bazoo apni taraf mila ley pus yeh dono moajzzay teray liye teray rab ki taraf say hain firaon aur uss ki jamat ki taraf yaqeenan woh sab kay sab bey hukum aur na farman log hain
